1.0.name: wordpress/space-manager
1.0.description: Wordpress' built-in text widget is great, but it's not all that user-friendly. Space Manager let's you use the familiar Wordpress' post editor to create "Spaces" and organize them into "Zones". You can drop these Zones into any sidebar and customize how you want to display them.
